<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>激活失败</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #ff6b6b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            animation: bounceIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        
        .error-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            fill: white;
        }
        
        .title {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }
        
        .error-details {
            background: #fff5f5;
            border: 1px solid #fed7d7;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }
        
        .error-details h3 {
            color: #c53030;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .error-details p {
            color: #742a2a;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .actions {
            margin-top: 40px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.8s both;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e9ecef;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .help-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f7fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4299e1;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 1s both;
        }
        
        .help-section h4 {
            color: #2b6cb0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .help-section ul {
            text-align: left;
            color: #2c5282;
            line-height: 1.8;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #edf2f7;
            border-radius: 12px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 1.2s both;
        }
        
        .contact-info h4 {
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-info p {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 1.4s both;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.3);
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
            70% {
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 20px;
                margin: 10px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M19,6.41L17.59,5L12,10.59L6.41,5L5,6.41L10.59,12L5,17.59L6.41,19L12,13.41L17.59,19L19,17.59L13.41,12L19,6.41Z"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        
        <div class="status-badge">❌ 激活失败</div>
        
        <h1 class="title">{{ error_title|default("激活失败") }}</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Opps，激活账户时出错啦XwX</p>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <h3>
                ⚠️ 错误详情
            </h3>
            <p>{{ error_message|default("激活链接无效或已过期，请重新申请激活邮件。") }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="help-section">
            <h4>💡 可能的解决方案</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>检查激活链接是否完整（避免被邮件客户端截断）</li>
                <li>尝试重新申请激活邮件，注意激活有效期</li>
                <li>检查垃圾邮件文件夹</li>
                <li>确认邮箱地址是否正确，用户信息是否无误</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <h4>📞 需要帮助？</h4>
            <p><strong>技术支持邮箱：</strong> {{ support_email|default("support@example.com") }}</p>
            <p><strong>客服时间：</strong> 工作日 9:00-18:00</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>🔒 如果您持续遇到问题，请保存此页面并联系我们</p>
            <p>错误代码: ACT_ERROR_{{ error_code|default("001") }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 记录错误信息用于调试
        console.error('激活失败:', {
            error: '{{ error_title }}',
            message: '{{ error_message }}',
            timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
